==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto "[[mano]]" and "[[konteno]]"
===Noun===
[[Category:Esperanto nouns]]
#A fastening, consisting of an iron ring around the wrist, usually connected by a chain with one on the other wrist; a manacle.

